// Pure component
// Ye ek feature ha jo hum import karke use karte hei per ye srf class components ke liye hota a
// pure component, component ke re-rendering ko rokta ha jese hum ne btn click se name change karwaya per wo name same ha pahle jesa to ye pahle check karega agr wo same ha to re-rendering nae karwayega warna karwayega.
